<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2021 09:41:05 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>AMG GLA 35 4MATIC 抵港，加入多款駕駛模式</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/15/amggla354matic/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=amggla354matic</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2021 09:39:45 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[AMG]]></category><category><![CDATA[benz]]></category><category><![CDATA[GLA 35 4MATIC]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1075939</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Mercedes Benz 新推出的 GLA 35 4MATIC 近日正式在香港公開發售，加入 5 種 AMG  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Mercedes Benz 新推出的 GLA 35 4MATIC 近日正式在香港公開發售，加入 5 種 AMG DYNAMIC SELECT 駕駛模式及 3 款避震系統，為駕駛者提供更大選擇靈活性。</p><p>GLA 35 4MATIC 為 Benz Mercedes-AMG 新推出的 35 系列輕巧車型，同樣裝有 AMG 獨有車頭格柵。而 GLA 35 4MATIC 的前分流器、窗框、外置後視鏡及後擾流裙等外觀為高光澤黑色，亦加入黑色的車頂行李架及排氣管裝飾，另配備 AMG 十幅式低風阻輕合金輪圈及 235/50 R 19 輪胎。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075940" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3-1280x720.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3-1536x864.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-3.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075941" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-694x520.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="520" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-694x520.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/AMG-Aerodynamics-Package-2-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075945 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_017-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075946 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_013-1-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075947 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-1280x852.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-768x511.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-1536x1023.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-2048x1364.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/20C0332_015-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而車內的儀表板共有 3 款設計選擇，包括「Classic」、「Sport」及「Supersport」，並由 MBUX 資訊娛樂系統提供 AMG 獨享的內容，更可於目錄中顯示「Warm-up」、「Set-up」、「G-Force」及「Engine data」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075942 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0991_008-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1075943 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-2048x1536.jpg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/19C0946_090-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>GLA 35 4MATIC 配備 2.0 公升直列 4 汽缸雙渦流渦輪增壓引擎，馬力輸出為 306 匹的 GLA 35 4MATIC 引擎扭力輸出可達 400 牛頓米。配合 AMG Performance 4MATIC 四驅系統驅動，傳動為 AMG SPEEDSHIFT DCT 8G 雙離合器波箱。只需 5.1 秒便可將車速由 0 加至 100 公里/小時。在電子限速的功能下，其極速為 250 公里/小時，每 100 公里的綜合耗油量是 7.5 至 7.6 升。</p><p>RACE-START 功能令 GLA 35 4MATIC 在加速的情況下能保持座駕靜止。另外亦提供 「Slippery」、「Comfort」、「Sport」、「Sport+」及「Individual」5 種 AMG DYNAMIC SELECT 駕駛模式，和「Comfort」、「Sport」及「Sport+」的避震系統讓駕駛者選擇。</p><p>GLA 35 4MATIC 香港售價由 HK$709,238 起。買家可選用「優選分期計劃」付款，每月約供 HK$8,012.1，共分 36 個月，費用已計算 20% 的首期車價。</p><p>規格</p><p>引擎：2.0 公升直列 4 汽缸雙渦流渦輪增壓引擎</p><p>驅動系統： AMG Performance 4MATIC 四驅系統</p><p>傳動： AMG SPEEDSHIFT DCT 8G 雙離合器波箱</p><p>引擎容量： 1,991 毫升</p><p>引擎馬力輸出： 306 匹； 每分鐘轉速 5800</p><p>引擎扭力輸出： 400 牛頓米； 每分鐘轉速 3,000-4,000</p><p>綜合耗油量： 7.5-7.6 升/100 公里</p><p>0-100 公里/小時加速： 5.1 秒</p><p>極速： 250 公里/小時 (電子限速)</p><p>售價： HK$709,238</p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
