</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日男製電子敲缽助檔案超渡，死機、彈 App 即自動敲缽</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/15/computer/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=computer</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2021 07:45:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1075676</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>相信常利用電腦工作的人一定會遇上電腦「死機」、畫面白屏的情況，若辛苦做的檔案、報告沒有即時存檔，努力的心血將會 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>相信常利用電腦工作的人一定會遇上電腦「死機」、畫面白屏的情況，若辛苦做的檔案、報告沒有即時存檔，努力的心血將會全數消失，使人深感心痛。</p><p>在日本推特（Twitter）上，一名網友分享了一段影片，當中展示了一件自製的敲缽，在電腦「死機」時幫助檔案超渡。</p><p>該名網友自製的機器以和尚敲缽的外型做為基礎，利用送輸線連接自製敲缽和電腦。當電腦當機、白屏時，這台機器就會敲缽，發出清脆的鈴聲，就像和尚在誠心念誦一樣，準備超渡死而不復返的檔案。影片的最後，該名網名友更雙手合緊，充滿儀式感。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075678" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-694x397.png" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-694x397.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-1280x733.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-768x440.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-1536x879.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53-2048x1172.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.16.53.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>      (資料圖片來源：Twitter@Argon_halide)<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075682" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-694x386.png" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-694x386.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-1280x712.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-768x427.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-1536x854.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1-2048x1139.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.17.21-1.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> </a>     (資料圖片來源：Twitter@Argon_halide)<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1075683" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-694x447.png" alt="" width="694" height="447" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-694x447.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-1280x824.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-768x495.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-1536x989.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00-2048x1319.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-13-18.18.00.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>     (資料圖片來源：Twitter@Argon_halide)</p><p>有其他網友看到影片後紛紛表示：「太搞笑了，確實是不錯的建議」、「這樣電腦應該也要一起超生吧」、「這個時機點太好了」，稱讚其十分有創意。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="ja" dir="ltr">データがご臨終したことを知らせてくれるデバイスを作りました <a href="https://t.co/jVzsV22UiR">pic.twitter.com/jVzsV22UiR</a></p><p>&mdash; アルゴンらんぷ (@Argon_halide) <a href="https://twitter.com/Argon_halide/status/1469248151836332033?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">December 10, 2021</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><div class="css-kqrvku"><div class="css-rd2992" data-is-focusable="false"><div class="css-l17e3k" data-is-focusable="true"><div id="mid.$cAAAAADDec1uDL1VtEF8_hAjUykVD" class="css-s1jfiq" dir="auto"><div class="css-kl86x4">資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/Argon_halide/status/1469248151836332033">Twitter@Argon_halide</a></div><div class="css-kl86x4">—</div><div class="css-16zmdoi" data-is-focusable="true">unwire.hk Mewe 專頁：<a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="css-kqrvku"><div class="css-rd2992" data-is-focusable="false"><div class="css-1paixk" data-is-focusable="true"><div class="css-8xttpl"><div class="css-1r9vq49"><div class="loaded-container css-1q9rghl loaded-container-enter-done"><div class="css-3z7cw8"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></p><div class="feedflare">
